- countries:
	- Ein Spieler(mit mindestens einer Stadt) kann ein "country" gründen und andere Städte einladen -> Zusammenschluss von Städten
	- bonus effects
		- shared plot amount
		- shared value
		- general spawn point
- something like power and water supply for cities -> can be traded inside of a country
- environment/green score:
	- capture number of leaves(and other blocks)
	- minus number of furnaces(and other blocks)
	-> score
	- bonus effects for positive score (speed, haste, ...)
	- negative effects for negative score (slow, foggy view, ...)
	- only city wide
	- capture -> block place, tree grow, block break

- time checking
	- scheduler -> every 60 seconds
	- safe current date
	- check date with last saved date -> difference? -> start new day
- hotels!